          <div class="hero-tagline">
            <span class="hero-tagline-dot"></span>
            Vision &amp; Origin
          </div>
          <h1 class="hero-heading">
            Building the readiness layer Japan deserves.
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-sub">
            TASK L3C exists to strengthen preparedness before the next major disaster —
            so Japan’s frontline NGOs and NPOs can act immediately with support already in place.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-ctas">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/programs.html">See the operating model</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact.html">Talk with TASK</a>
